When Clayton was 9 months old, Buddy abused Clayton, He throwed Clayton's poop in his bed, From his fear, He ran off

In 2022, He tried to show Buddy love but he abused, Such as threatened with a punishment, etc.

In 2023, Clayton rummaged the garbage, Which ended up Buddy neuter him,

In 2024, Clayton tried of Buddy's abuse, When His owner abused him he sprayed, Which ended up seizing him to animal control, 3 months later he escaped,

2025, Clayton tried to wander Espinoza residence but he got hit by a car, Ended up killing Kim

